description.displayText: Yahaira, is extremely nice, caring, careful and excited when dealing with kids.I have a 3yr old and a 5 month old and they love her. She has put effort when helping my 3yr old learn to write her name and read to her almost every time. She is extremely clean and careful when dealing with the kids,their food and while working in my home. I will recommend Yahaira to work with my friends, family and anyone's kids who need a babysitter.
